dc_title_s: Plan no. 1 of lots of Silver Bay,Township of Dover, Ocean County, New Jersey
dc_description_s: The map is a negative photostat that shows property lots in the Silver Bay area between Main Street and Barnegat Bay and Silver Bay Harbor. It has two attached enlargements stapled.|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|Handwritten inscription in lower right corner states Map File 112-1A.|Dover Township, Ocean County changed its name to Toms River in 2006.
